OL,3,CMystery #1k donation posted through
OL,4,Ccharity's letterbox
OL,6,FStaff at a charity in Bristol say they
OL,7,Fwere "knocked off their chairs" after
OL,8,Ffinding a wad of old #20 notes
OL,9,Ftotalling more than #1,000 posted
OL,10,Fthrough their letterbox.
OL,12,FThe charity, which supports parents
OL,13,Fand carers of autistic children,
OL,14,Freceived the money anonymously by post
OL,15,Fon 4 June.
OL,17,FJade Page, the charity's Parent
OL,18,FSupport Manager, found the donation
OL,19,Fwhile she was sifting through the post.
