OL,6,F"On Tuesday afternoon I collected our
OL,7,Fpost from reception as normal. One
OL,8,Fenvelope was sellotaped up and
OL,9,Fdifficult to open, I very nearly
OL,10,Fripped it" she said.
OL,12,F"Out spilled #1,020 all in old #20
OL,13,Fbank notes. In my excitement I didn't
OL,14,Fspot they were old notes. This was the
OL,15,Ffirst thing one of my finance
OL,16,Fcolleagues noticed.
