OL,3,CMystery #1k donation posted through
OL,4,Ccharity's letterbox
OL,6,F"I checked with the reception team and
OL,7,Fthe envelope definitely came in with
OL,8,Fthe usual post. There was no postmark
OL,9,Fon it, although it was stamped and had
OL,10,Fa small mark over the stamp suggesting
OL,11,Fit was posted.
OL,13,F"I rushed to get the post office
OL,14,Fbefore they close and was thrilled
OL,15,Fwhen they confirmed the notes were
OL,16,Freal and could be paid in.
OL,18,F"A wonderful surprise for us as a
OL,19,Fsmall charity where donations make a
OL,20,Fhuge difference."
