OL,6,FThe charity says the donation will go
OL,7,Ftowards supporting its working
OL,8,Fincluding free in-person support, a
OL,9,Fhelpline, training and information
OL,10,Fsessions and family events.
OL,12,FBristol Autism Support is the third
OL,13,Fcharity in the region to receive such
OL,14,Fa donation, following Marie Curie in
OL,15,FBristol last month and the RNLI in
OL,16,FPortishead in April.
